
This directory contains the nessesary configure files and scripts to
build a simple template module (src/template.mx) for the monet database engine.

Before continuing find (or compile) a monet version 4.2 or higher.

set MONET_PREFIX

export MONET_PREFIX=`./monet-config --prefix`

run bootstrap in the top directory
mkdir $ARCH
cd $ARCH
../configure --prefix=`pwd` 
gmake -j
gmake install

add the modules directory to your MONET_MOD_PATH and LD_LIBRARY_PATH

ie. export MONET_MOD_PATH=`pwd`/lib/template:$MONET_MOD_PATH
    export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=`pwd`/lib/template:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH

Read the monet manual for creating a database and starting a monet server

Mserver -db template
module(template);
avg( dbl(2.0), ZERO).print;


